# Pilot-bench writes one `pilot_result_<timestamp>/` directory per
# round, with raw readings and session logs. The Markdown summary at
# benchmarks/pilot_ss_latest.md is the artefact we keep; everything
# else is recomputed by re-running scripts/bench_pilot.sh.
/pilot_result_*

# Outputs from examples/verify_ship.sh — share images for visual
